text: Julija Kovaliova (born 20 December 1980) is a Lithuanian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Lithuanian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Lithuania Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vilnius
